==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Minify
<hw>Min"i*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p.
p.</pos> <conjf>Minified</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Minifying</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>minor</ets> less + <ets>-fly</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To make small, or smaller; to diminish the apparent
dimensions of; to lessen.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To degrade by speech or action.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Minikin</ent>⟦br⟧
